# Gongbu Platform - Frontend Rules

## React Development

### ✅ МОЖНО
- Functional components с hooks
- TypeScript для всех компонентов
- Custom hooks для reusable logic
- useMemo/useCallback для optimization
- Error boundaries для error handling
- Lazy loading для code splitting
- React DevTools для debugging
- Storybook для component documentation

### ❌ НЕЛЬЗЯ
- Class components (используй functional)
- Inline styles (используй CSS modules или styled-components)  
- Props drilling больше 2 уровней
- useEffect без cleanup
- State mutations (всегда immutable updates)
- Keys как array indexes для динамических списков
- Memory leaks через event listeners

## State Management

### ✅ МОЖНО
- Redux Toolkit для global state
- RTK Query для server state
- Local state для component-specific data
- Context API для theme и user preferences
- Normalized state structure
- Action creators с type safety
- Selectors для derived state

### ❌ НЕЛЬЗЯ
- Redux без Redux Toolkit
- Putting everything в global state
- Mutating state directly
- Large objects в component state
- Async operations в reducers
- Complex state logic в components
- State updates без proper batching

## UI/UX Guidelines

### ✅ МОЖНО
- Material-UI (MUI) components
- Responsive design (mobile-first)
- Loading states для async operations
- Error states с retry options
- Accessibility (WCAG guidelines)
- Consistent spacing и typography
- Theme provider для consistent styling

### ❌ НЕЛЬЗЯ
- Custom UI components без необходимости
- Desktop-only design
- Missing loading indicators
- Poor error messages
- Inaccessible components (missing ARIA)
- Inconsistent visual hierarchy
- Hardcoded colors или spacing

## Performance

### ✅ МОЖНО
- Code splitting по routes
- Lazy loading для heavy components  
- Image optimization и lazy loading
- Bundle analysis (webpack-bundle-analyzer)
- Virtualization для long lists
- Memoization для expensive calculations
- Service workers для caching

### ❌ НЕЛЬЗЯ
- Large bundle sizes без optimization
- Unnecessary re-renders
- Loading all images at once
- Blocking main thread
- Memory leaks в components
- Unused dependencies в bundle
- Synchronous operations в UI

## Forms & Validation

### ✅ МОЖНО
- React Hook Form для form handling
- Yup или Zod для validation schemas
- Controlled components для critical inputs
- Debounced validation для better UX
- Clear error messages
- Form state persistence где нужно
- Accessibility для form controls

### ❌ НЕЛЬЗЯ
- Uncontrolled forms для complex scenarios
- Client-side only validation
- Poor validation error messaging
- Forms без loading states
- Missing form labels
- Auto-submit без user confirmation
- Form data в URL parameters